         <Summary>TBoldCustomTreeView allows displaying and optionally editing information from the Business Object tier of Bold.</Summary>
         <Desc>It is a subclass of TCustomTreeView.
See the TBoldTreeView for a general description.
            <BH>Implementation</BH>
TBoldCustomTreeView keeps most of its properties protected. It is not intended to be used directly, but rather to be subclassed, where the subclasses publish and/or override the behaviour implemented by TBoldCustomTreeView. </Desc>
